result.adr_address: 321 Des Voeux Rd W, Sai Ying Pun, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 321 Des Voeux Rd W, Sai Ying Pun, Hong Kong
result.name: NOC Roastery

reviews.text:
Absolutely lovely coffee shop. The coffee is fantastic and the staff is knowledgeable and kind. 
The place features great ambiance, with a modern decor and soft background music (just the right volume to let you talk without interruptions). The coffee roasting equipment is visible near the entrance yet the smell is not overwhelming.
A great place to enjoy a cup of coffee and chill.

Really good crossiant! Almost as good as from a french bakery. Super flaky. 
Cold brew coffee is a must try. 
Good quality food and service. Definitely will return. 
Don’t bother going to Causeway Bay shop, staff there are not friendly nor very helpful.

Great location and a peaceful place for work! There are also very friendly people who also speak English! The coffee is delicious, so just take a large container.  The difference is only 5 dollars (0.6 cents). Advice is therefore to order coffee with food.  Such as the avocado toast, or something else tasty. The coffee is then for half the price!  Abosulte recommended this place!

Finally here to try the food! Portion seems small but actually very filling. Coffee is consistently good.  
It has a positive atmosphere as a communal work space.  People respect the quietness.  Recommended! And look forward to the other branch soon opening in Tin Hau.

Ultra chic cafe! Looks like a lab paired with an Apple store and NOC came out as a baby. Cool audience, tasty snacks, brutally good coffee. Not surprised that the chain already has 6 stores all over Hong Kong.
